SELECT DISTINCT
  i_product_name
FROM item AS i1
INNER JOIN manufacturer_counts AS mc
  ON i1.i_manufact = mc.i_manufact
WHERE
  i_manufact_id BETWEEN 748 AND 788 AND mc.item_cnt > 0
ORDER BY
  i_product_name
LIMIT 100

WITH manufacturer_counts AS (
  SELECT
    i_manufact,
    COUNT(
      CASE
        WHEN i_category = 'Women'
        AND i_color IN ('gainsboro', 'aquamarine')
        AND i_units IN ('Ounce', 'Dozen')
        AND i_size IN ('medium', 'economy')
        THEN 1
      END
    ) AS cnt1,
    COUNT(
      CASE
        WHEN i_category = 'Women'
        AND i_color IN ('chiffon', 'violet')
        AND i_units IN ('Ton', 'Pound')
        AND i_size IN ('extra large', 'small')
        THEN 1
      END
    ) AS cnt2,
    COUNT(
      CASE
        WHEN i_category = 'Men'
        AND i_color IN ('chartreuse', 'blue')
        AND i_units IN ('Each', 'Oz')
        AND i_size IN ('N/A', 'large')
        THEN 1
      END
    ) AS cnt3,
    COUNT(
      CASE
        WHEN i_category = 'Men'
        AND i_color IN ('tan', 'dodger')
        AND i_units IN ('Bunch', 'Tsp')
        AND i_size IN ('medium', 'economy')
        THEN 1
      END
    ) AS cnt4,
    COUNT(
      CASE
        WHEN i_category = 'Women'
        AND i_color IN ('blanched', 'tomato')
        AND i_units IN ('Tbl', 'Case')
        AND i_size IN ('medium', 'economy')
        THEN 1
      END
    ) AS cnt5,
    COUNT(
      CASE
        WHEN i_category = 'Women'
        AND i_color IN ('almond', 'lime')
        AND i_units IN ('Box', 'Dram')
        AND i_size IN ('extra large', 'small')
        THEN 1
      END
    ) AS cnt6,
    COUNT(
      CASE
        WHEN i_category = 'Men'
        AND i_color IN ('peru', 'saddle')
        AND i_units IN ('Pallet', 'Gram')
        AND i_size IN ('N/A', 'large')
        THEN 1
      END
    ) AS cnt7,
    COUNT(
      CASE
        WHEN i_category = 'Men'
        AND i_color IN ('indian', 'spring')
        AND i_units IN ('Unknown', 'Carton')
        AND i_size IN ('medium', 'economy')
        THEN 1
      END
    ) AS cnt8
  FROM item
  WHERE
    i_category IN ('Women', 'Men')
    AND i_color IN (
      'gainsboro',
      'aquamarine',
      'chiffon',
      'violet',
      'chartreuse',
      'blue',
      'tan',
      'dodger',
      'blanched',
      'tomato',
      'almond',
      'lime',
      'peru',
      'saddle',
      'indian',
      'spring'
    )
    AND i_units IN (
      'Ounce',
      'Dozen',
      'Ton',
      'Pound',
      'Each',
      'Oz',
      'Bunch',
      'Tsp',
      'Tbl',
      'Case',
      'Box',
      'Dram',
      'Pallet',
      'Gram',
      'Unknown',
      'Carton'
    )
    AND i_size IN ('medium', 'economy', 'extra large', 'small', 'N/A', 'large')
  GROUP BY
    i_manufact
  HAVING
    cnt1 > 0
    OR cnt2 > 0
    OR cnt3 > 0
    OR cnt4 > 0
    OR cnt5 > 0
    OR cnt6 > 0
    OR cnt7 > 0
    OR cnt8 > 0
)
